    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      I bought this March 2, 2025 and it's now December 1, 2025. I now use the Yagud nearly every single day. This walking pad has performed perfectly, without any stuttering, without any shutdowns, 100% of the time. It's been a perfectly performing walking pad.
